Document: VisualShaderNodeParticleRingEmitter
Path: godot/classes/class_visualshadernodeparticleringemitter.rst
Summary: A VisualShaderNodeParticleEmitter that emits particles in a ring shape with specified inner and outer radii and height.

VisualShaderNodeParticleRingEmitter is a VisualShaderNodeParticleEmitter that makes the particles emitted in ring shape with the specified inner and outer radii and height.